        "body": "<p>The answer is that <strong>you cannot do what you are trying to do<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n<p>You cannot use a <code>switch<\/code> statement for this.<\/p>\n\n<p>Use an <code>if<\/code> statement instead.<\/p>\n",
